sim_data <- readRDS("expected_single_sim.rds")

obs_only <- sim_data %>%
  unnest(subj_obs) %>%
  select(subj_index = subj, 
         error = obs_radian,
         obs_degree, 
         stimulation)

fit brms

# define prior
# priors

bprior <- prior(normal(4, 0.5), class = "b", coef = "intercept", dpar = "circSD") + 
  prior(normal(0, 0.5), class = "b", coef = "stimulation", dpar = "circSD") +
  prior(normal(0, 0.5), class = "sd", coef = "Intercept", dpar = "circSD", group = "subj_index") + 
  prior(normal(0, 0.5), class = "sd", coef = "stimulation", dpar = "circSD", group = "subj_index") + 
  prior(normal(0, 1.5), class = "b", coef = "intercept", dpar = "theta") + 
  prior(normal(0, 1), class = "b", coef = "stimulation", dpar = "theta") +
  prior(normal(0, 1.5), class = "sd", coef = "Intercept", dpar = "theta", group = "subj_index") + 
  prior(normal(0, 1), class = "sd", coef = "stimulation", dpar = "theta", group = "subj_index")


model_fit <- brm(bform, obs_only, family = vm_uniform_mix, prior = bprior, stanvars = stanvars,
                 warmup = 1000, iter = 2000, cores = 4, chains = 4, control = list(adapt_delta = 0.99), inits = 0, 
                 file = "model_fit")

posterior_array <- as.array(model_fit$fit)

print(model_fit)
##  Family: vm_uniform_mix 
##   Links: mu = identity; circSD = log; theta = logit; a = identity; b = identity 
## Formula: error ~ 0 
##          circSD ~ 0 + intercept + stimulation + (1 + stimulation || subj_index)
##          theta ~ 0 + intercept + stimulation + (1 + stimulation || subj_index)
##          a = -3.14
##          b = 3.14
##    Data: obs_only (Number of observations: 756) 
## Samples: 4 chains, each with iter = 2000; warmup = 1000; thin = 1;
##          total post-warmup samples = 4000
##

#check neff and rhat and divergences
np <- nuts_params(model_fit)
rhat <- brms::rhat(model_fit)
neff_rat <- neff_ratio(model_fit)

np %>% 
  filter(Parameter == "divergent__") %>%
  summarise(n_div = sum(Value))

# compute summaries for plot

group_level_samples <- spread_draws(model_fit, `b_.*`, regex = TRUE) %>%
  transmute(circSD_pre_mean = exp(b_circSD_intercept),
            circSD_post_mean = exp(b_circSD_intercept + b_circSD_stimulation),
            circSD_ES_mean = circSD_post_mean - circSD_pre_mean,
            pMem_pre_mean = inv_logit(b_theta_intercept),
            pMem_post_mean = inv_logit(b_theta_intercept + b_theta_stimulation),
            pMem_ES_mean = pMem_post_mean - pMem_pre_mean) %>% 
  pivot_longer(everything(), names_to = "param", values_to = "value")

group_level_summary <- group_level_samples %>%
  group_by(param) %>%
  median_qi(.width = c(.90, .95))
## Warning: unnest() has a new interface. See ?unnest for details.
## Try `df %>% unnest(c(.lower, .upper))`, with `mutate()` if needed

## Warning: unnest() has a new interface. See ?unnest for details.
## Try `df %>% unnest(c(.lower, .upper))`, with `mutate()` if needed
circSD_subj_samples <- model_fit %>%
  spread_draws(b_circSD_intercept, b_circSD_stimulation, r_subj_index__circSD[subj, term]) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = term, values_from = r_subj_index__circSD, names_prefix = "offset_") %>%
  transmute(subj = subj,
            subj_circSD_pre = exp(b_circSD_intercept + offset_Intercept),
            subj_circSD_post = exp(b_circSD_intercept + offset_Intercept + b_circSD_stimulation + offset_stimulation),
            subj_circSD_ES = subj_circSD_post - subj_circSD_pre) %>%
  pivot_longer(contains("circSD"), names_to = "param", values_to = "value") 

circSD_subj_summary <- circSD_subj_samples %>%
  group_by(subj, param) %>%
  median_qi(.width = c(.90, .95))
## Warning: unnest() has a new interface. See ?unnest for details.
## Try `df %>% unnest(c(.lower, .upper))`, with `mutate()` if needed

## Warning: unnest() has a new interface. See ?unnest for details.
## Try `df %>% unnest(c(.lower, .upper))`, with `mutate()` if needed
pMem_subj_samples <- model_fit %>%
  spread_draws(b_theta_intercept, b_theta_stimulation, r_subj_index__theta[subj, term]) %>%
  ungroup() %>%
  pivot_wider(names_from = term, values_from = r_subj_index__theta, names_prefix = "offset_") %>%
  transmute(subj = subj,
            subj_pMem_pre = inv_logit(b_theta_intercept + offset_Intercept),
            subj_pMem_post = inv_logit(b_theta_intercept + offset_Intercept + b_theta_stimulation + offset_stimulation),
            subj_pMem_ES = subj_pMem_post - subj_pMem_pre) %>%
  pivot_longer(contains("pMem"), names_to = "param", values_to = "value")

pMem_subj_summary <- pMem_subj_samples %>%
  group_by(subj, param) %>%
  median_qi(.width = c(.90, .95))

circSD pre, post, ES

circSD_p1 <- group_level_samples %>% 
  filter(str_detect(param, "circSD")) %>%
  ggplot(aes(y = param, x = value)) + 
  geom_halfeyeh(.width = c(.90, .95)) + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = pretty_breaks(10)) + 
  labs(subtitle = "circSD: group level parameters")
  
circSD_p2 <- rbind(
  group_level_samples %>% 
    filter(str_detect(param, "circSD_pre"))
  ,
  circSD_subj_samples %>%
    filter(str_detect(param, "circSD_pre")) %>%
    unite(param, param, subj)
  ) %>%
  ggplot(aes(y = param, x = value)) + 
  geom_halfeyeh(.width = c(.90, .95)) + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = pretty_breaks(10)) + 
  labs(subtitle = "circSD_pre: group level parameter + subject estimates")

circSD_p3 <- rbind(
  group_level_samples %>% 
    filter(str_detect(param, "circSD_post"))
  ,
  circSD_subj_samples %>%
    filter(str_detect(param, "circSD_post")) %>%
    unite(param, param, subj)
  ) %>%
  ggplot(aes(y = param, x = value)) + 
  geom_halfeyeh(.width = c(.90, .95)) + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = pretty_breaks(10)) + 
  labs(subtitle = "circSD_post: group level parameter + subject estimates")

circSD_p4 <- rbind(
  group_level_samples %>% 
    filter(str_detect(param, "circSD_ES"))
  ,
  circSD_subj_samples %>%
    filter(str_detect(param, "circSD_ES")) %>%
    unite(param, param, subj)
  ) %>%
  ggplot(aes(y = param, x = value)) + 
  geom_halfeyeh(.width = c(.90, .95)) + 
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = pretty_breaks(10)) + 
  labs(subtitle = "circSD_ES: group level parameter + subject estimates")

plot_grid(circSD_p1, circSD_p2, circSD_p3, circSD_p4, ncol = 1, align = "hv")

group level joint posteriors

fixed-effets

fixed_effects <- spread_draws(model_fit, `b_.*`, regex = TRUE)

fixed_effects_delink <- fixed_effects %>%
  transmute(circSD_pre = exp(b_circSD_intercept),
         circSD_post = exp(b_circSD_intercept + b_circSD_stimulation),
         pMem_pre = inv_logit(b_theta_intercept),
         pMem_post = inv_logit(b_theta_intercept + b_theta_stimulation))

plot_grid(
  
  fixed_effects_delink %>%
    transmute(circSD_pre,
           circSD_post,
           circSD_ES = circSD_post - circSD_pre) %>%
    gather(param, value) %>%
    ggplot(aes(x = value, y = param)) +
    geom_halfeyeh() + 
    scale_x_continuous(breaks = pretty_breaks(10))

    ,
  
    fixed_effects_delink %>%
    transmute(pMem_pre,
           pMem_post,
           pMem_ES = pMem_post - pMem_pre) %>%
    gather(param, value) %>%
    ggplot(aes(x = value, y = param)) +
    geom_halfeyeh() + 
    scale_x_continuous(breaks = pretty_breaks(10))
  ,
    
  ncol = 1
)
